#

Classic American Cobb Salad

15 min
$12.5
450 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

DairyEggs

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main

Tags:

SaladHealthyQuick

Description

A fresh and vibrant salad packed with flavors and textures, perfect for a light meal.

Ingredients

  • romaine lettuce: 4 cups, chopped
  • cooked chicken breast: 1 cup, diced
  • hard-boiled eggs: 2, chopped
  • bacon: 4 slices, cooked and crumbled
  • cherry tomatoes: 1 cup, halved
  • avocado: 1, diced
  • blue cheese: 1/2 cup, crumbled
  • ranch dressing: 1/2 cup
